# lsmonitor
lsmonitor script for LS-CHL with debian

Based on:
 blstools  - Copyright (C) 2010 Michele Manzato
 lsmonitor - Copyright (C) 2013 Sergej Wildemann

Credits:
 Thanks to archonfx on Buffalo NAS Central forum for HDD
 temperature monitoring command.


monitor the power switch and the function button
check hdd status and temperatur
set the fan speed

you can define a user function
this file will be executed if you press the function button
